              <h4>Community Impact & Recognition</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>106 GitHub stars, 78 forks - highest engagement in PageBuilder ecosystem</li>
                <li>Primary educational resource for PageBuilder developers worldwide</li>
                <li>Created 10+ example modules covering major use cases</li>
                <li>Active community contributions and ongoing maintenance</li>
              </ul>
