    <div class="featured-documentation">
      <h2>Featured Live Documentation</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        Direct links to live documentation and interactive tools I've created and maintain at Adobe
        Commerce. These represent real-world examples of developer experience innovation in action.
      </p>

      <div class="documentation-grid grid-extra-large">
        <div class="doc-card">
          <div class="doc-header">
            <h3>API Playground</h3>
            <div class="doc-status">🚀 Live</div>
          </div>
          <div class="doc-description">
            <p>
              Interactive playground providing hands-on experience with Adobe Commerce services.
              Features predefined queries that developers can run and customize to explore our APIs
              in greater detail.
            </p>
            <div class="doc-highlights">
              <ul>
                <li>Real-time API testing environment</li>
                <li>Predefined query examples</li>
                <li>Customizable exploration tools</li>
                <li>Integrated developer learning experience</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="doc-links">
              <a
